<plot>A young college student, Dave Jewell, wakes to find Death in his dorm room, forcing Dave to examine his under-achieving, low-aiming life. Together they decide to fulfill Dave's life ambitions, culminating in telling Sunshine his feelings he's felt for her since middle school. Ironically, Dave experiences his most care-free, life-giving day of his existence on the day of his death, leaving him searching for a legacy.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?216464</url></doc>
